00:17:19,755 --> 00:17:22,055
Are you done yet?

262
00:17:22,055 --> 00:17:23,794
- I'm done.
- Yes.

263
00:17:23,794 --> 00:17:25,155
Okay.

264
00:17:25,955 --> 00:17:27,855
Come on.

265
00:17:27,855 --> 00:17:29,474
Answer whichever one you draw.

266
00:17:29,475 --> 00:17:31,175
I'll go first.

267
00:17:34,925 --> 00:17:37,475
Knock Xue on her forehead.

268
00:17:40,085 --> 00:17:41,914
Zhang Qi, it must be you.

269
00:17:41,914 --> 00:17:44,185
Just admit defeat.

270
00:17:46,085 --> 00:17:49,264
- I'm sorry, Xue.
- Do it softly.

271
00:17:49,264 --> 00:17:50,474
Be harder.

272
00:17:50,475 --> 00:17:53,405
Three, two...

273
00:17:54,165 --> 00:17:55,865
one.

274
00:17:59,675 --> 00:18:01,405
I took it for Xue.

275
00:18:01,405 --> 00:18:02,924
Sunian is so nice.

276
00:18:02,925 --> 00:18:04,925
It's my turn.

277
00:18:11,125 --> 00:18:12,925
No.

278
00:18:14,755 --> 00:18:16,755
What's written on it?

279
00:18:16,755 --> 00:18:18,155
There's nothing.

280
00:18:22,195 --> 00:18:25,995
Please describe your first kiss in detail.

281
00:18:27,645 --> 00:18:29,605
There's none.

282
00:18:29,605 --> 00:18:31,665
Tell the truth.

283
00:18:33,325 --> 00:18:35,315
You'd better keep it up.

284
00:18:35,315 --> 00:18:37,325
It's my turn.

285
00:18:41,935 --> 00:18:44,035
More than ten.

286
00:18:46,435 --> 00:18:50,305
"How many love letters have you ever received?"

287
00:18:52,135 --> 00:18:54,474
Although the amount is incredible,

288
00:18:54,474 --> 00:18:57,174
it's not surprising for Sunian.

289
00:18:57,174 --> 00:18:58,754
I think so, too.

290
00:18:58,755 --> 00:19:01,625
Why haven't I received one?

291
00:19:01,625 --> 00:19:04,854
That's because thegirls in our school do well in eye exercises.

292
00:19:04,854 --> 00:19:05,885
Get out.

293
00:19:05,886 --> 00:19:08,525
All right! It's Wu Huan's turn.

294
00:19:08,525 --> 00:19:10,275
Okay.

295
00:19:11,715 --> 00:19:15,195
Hug the people around you.

296
00:19:30,815 --> 00:19:33,025
Okay, it's done.

297
00:19:38,805 --> 00:19:41,285
Why are you looking at me? It's your turn.

298
00:19:42,335 --> 00:19:44,235
Oh, it's my turn.

299
00:19:58,365 --> 00:19:59,965
Shao Xue.

300
00:20:02,745 --> 00:20:04,885
I like you.

301
00:20:17,425 --> 00:20:19,975
What's wrong with you all? I was just kidding.

302
00:20:19,975 --> 00:20:21,195
You scared me.

303
00:20:21,195 --> 00:20:23,035
It's written on it.

304
00:20:23,035 --> 00:20:25,625
"Tell a lie that you dare not say."

305
00:20:25,625 --> 00:20:27,955
Zhang Qi, you're excellent at acting.

306
00:20:27,955 --> 00:20:29,895
Don't mention it.

307
00:20:33,645 --> 00:20:35,645
Who's calling at this time?

308
00:20:36,405 --> 00:20:39,605
My mom. Don't talk.

309
00:20:40,855 --> 00:20:43,915
- Hello, Mom.
<i>- Shao Xue, where have you been?</i>

310
00:20:43,915 --> 00:20:45,665
<i>You're going to piss me off, aren't you?</i>

311
00:20:45,665 --> 00:20:48,484
<i>Zhang Qi, you brat. Do you want to piss me off?</i>

312
00:20:48,484 --> 00:20:51,114
<i>Lin Shiyin, I won't believe you anymore.</i>

313
00:20:51,114 --> 00:20:53,415
<i>Xue, I'll break your legs.</i>

314
00:20:53,415 --> 00:20:54,994
<i>Come back now!</i>

315
00:20:54,995 --> 00:20:57,270
<i>[LIULI HUTONG]</i>

316
00:20:57,855 --> 00:20:59,685
<i>Get off.</i>

317
00:21:00,515 --> 00:21:01,915
Get off.

318
00:21:01,915 --> 00:21:04,020
Do I even have to invite you?

319
00:21:04,020 --> 00:21:05,025
- Take it easy.
- Get off.

320
00:21:05,025 --> 00:21:06,086
- Take it easy.
- Mom.

321
00:21:06,086 --> 00:21:08,055
What are you doing? There are many people watching.

322
00:21:08,055 --> 00:21:10,525
- I'll get you at home.
- Are you my birth mother?

323
00:21:10,525 --> 00:21:12,575
No. Your birth mother has been pissed off by you.

324
00:21:12,575 --> 00:21:14,655
- Let's go.
- Dad!
- Take it easy.

325
00:21:14,655 --> 00:21:16,924
Thank you for your hard work. Take it easy.

326
00:21:16,925 --> 00:21:18,625
Shiyin!

327
00:21:20,335 --> 00:21:21,465
Lin Shiyin.

328
00:21:21,465 --> 00:21:23,055
- Mom.
- You can still smile.

329
00:21:23,055 --> 00:21:24,025
Get off now.

330
00:21:24,025 --> 00:21:26,775
Mom, don't drag me. The clothes will get wrinkled.

331
00:21:26,775 --> 00:21:29,405
Don't you know your priorities yet?

332
00:21:29,405 --> 00:21:31,675
I was upset. I wanted to relax.

333
00:21:31,675 --> 00:21:33,404
You really pissed me off.

334
00:21:33,405 --> 00:21:35,325
- Take the suitcase.
- Get off.

335
00:21:35,325 --> 00:21:36,695
Let's go.

336
00:21:37,900 --> 00:21:40,225
<i>[Liuli Hutong Residents Committee]</i>

337
00:21:40,225 --> 00:21:42,405
Stop there, you brat.

338
00:21:43,085 --> 00:21:44,434
What a big mess you have made!

339
00:21:44,435 --> 00:21:46,185
What's wrong?

340
00:21:46,185 --> 00:21:49,755
I just didn't want to celebrate my birthday in the house alone.

341
00:21:49,755 --> 00:21:52,565
Talk well. Don't hit him.

342
00:21:52,565 --> 00:21:54,985
You can tell me your thoughts.

343
00:21:54,985 --> 00:21:57,475
Can I even find you?

344
00:21:57,475 --> 00:21:59,055
Didn't you say three days?

345
00:21:59,055 --> 00:22:01,025
Why did you come back today?

346
00:22:01,025 --> 00:22:02,805
It was to celebrate your birthday.

347
00:22:02,806 --> 00:22:04,674
But you made a mess.

348
00:22:04,675 --> 00:22:06,704
- Let's go.
- I'm not going back.

349
00:22:06,704 --> 00:22:08,985
- Come on.
- No!

350
00:22:10,505 --> 00:22:12,875
- I'll write a self-criticism.
- I'm not going back.

351
00:22:12,875 --> 00:22:16,335
Try not to lie in the future, okay?

352
00:22:16,335 --> 00:22:17,844
Okay.

353
00:22:17,845 --> 00:22:20,035
All right then. Come on. Give it to me.

354
00:22:20,035 --> 00:22:22,415
Why didn't anyone scold him?

355
00:22:22,415 --> 00:22:24,615
You're indeed a busybody.

356
00:22:24,615 --> 00:22:28,665
Sunian never did anything bad. It was you who made him do something bad.

357
00:22:28,665 --> 00:22:30,235
- Let's go back.
- I was blamed for everything.

358
00:22:30,235 --> 00:22:31,836
- I don't want to.
- Madam.

359
00:22:31,836 --> 00:22:35,765
Well. I want to say something to Zhang Qi.

360
00:22:35,765 --> 00:22:36,754
Okay.

361
00:22:36,755 --> 00:22:38,735
Come back early. Do you hear me?

362
00:22:38,735 --> 00:22:41,324
- Go home early.
- Yes, Madam.

363
00:22:50,955 --> 00:22:52,185
She's not home every day.

364
00:22:52,185 --> 00:22:53,945
Yet she quarrels with me once she comes back.

365
00:22:53,945 --> 00:22:55,265
Your mom is worried about you.

366
00:22:55,265 --> 00:22:57,165
What can she worry about?

367
00:23:00,305 --> 00:23:03,405
Oh, right. What do you want to tell me?

368
00:23:09,665 --> 00:23:11,165
Zhang Qi.

369
00:23:12,035 --> 00:23:15,235
I wrote the question.

370
00:23:15,235 --> 00:23:17,505
I know what was written inside.

371
00:23:32,665 --> 00:23:35,035
Aren't you going to tell her?

372
00:23:37,675 --> 00:23:39,475
I want to.

373
00:23:39,475 --> 00:23:41,324
But I don't know what to say.

374
00:23:41,325 --> 00:23:43,425
If I don't say it,

375
00:23:43,425 --> 00:23:46,235
I feel everything's hidden inside.

376
00:23:46,235 --> 00:23:48,565
I don't know what to do either.

377
00:23:48,565 --> 00:23:51,074
- Shall I help you tell her?
- No.

378
00:23:53,855 --> 00:23:57,545
I'm afraid if I say it,

379
00:23:58,085 --> 00:24:00,585
many things may change.

380
00:24:03,805 --> 00:24:07,515
Huanhuan, keep the secret for me first.

381
00:24:07,515 --> 00:24:09,015
Okay?

382
00:24:10,575 --> 00:24:11,844
You may go back.

383
00:24:11,845 --> 00:24:14,335
Okay, I'll get going.

384
00:24:14,335 --> 00:24:17,435
By the way, happy birthday.

385
00:24:17,435 --> 00:24:19,205
I'm going back. Goodbye.

386
00:24:31,020 --> 00:24:35,250
<i>[Tell the truth you dare not say]</i>

387
00:24:45,950 --> 00:24:50,130
<i>[Mailbox]</i>

388
00:25:04,745 --> 00:25:07,335
The milk is already warm. Drink it.

389
00:25:11,705 --> 00:25:13,975
What is Sunian doing?

390
00:25:13,975 --> 00:25:15,785
He's studying.

391
00:25:17,675 --> 00:25:21,335
He hides it quite deeply.

392
00:25:27,265 --> 00:25:29,065
Zheng.

393
00:25:29,985 --> 00:25:32,765
I'll go out of town next week

394
00:25:32,765 --> 00:25:35,205
to visit a distant relative.

395
00:25:35,205 --> 00:25:37,445
I'll stay there for a few days.

396
00:25:39,805 --> 00:25:41,234
Why is it so sudden?

397
00:25:41,235 --> 00:25:43,175
What happened?

398
00:25:45,675 --> 00:25:47,645
Nothing.

399
00:25:47,645 --> 00:25:49,475
We just got in touch.

400
00:25:49,475 --> 00:25:53,065
I want to take this chance to go out and relax.

401
00:25:56,575 --> 00:25:58,895
Have you been upset lately?

402
00:25:59,535 --> 00:26:01,265
No.

403
00:26:01,265 --> 00:26:04,374
I just want to travel. Can't I?

404
00:26:05,085 --> 00:26:06,685
No, you can.

405
00:26:06,685 --> 00:26:09,325
That's right. We haven't been out for a long time.

406
00:26:09,325 --> 00:26:11,754
After I'm done with the exhibition,

407
00:26:11,755 --> 00:26:13,375
let's take annual leave.

408
00:26:13,375 --> 00:26:15,355
We can go out and have fun for a few days.

409
00:26:15,355 --> 00:26:17,364
What are you thinking about?

410
00:26:17,365 --> 00:26:19,335
Sunian is now in Grade 12.

411
00:26:19,335 --> 00:26:21,805
Take care of him at home.

412
00:26:21,805 --> 00:26:27,815
Well. It's tough to be the parents of a 12th Grade kid.

413
00:26:27,815 --> 00:26:30,005
Go to bed early. You have to get up early tomorrow.

414
00:26:30,005 --> 00:26:31,755
Drink the milk.

415
00:26:54,915 --> 00:26:56,835
Sunian.

416
00:26:59,425 --> 00:27:01,405
Sunian.

417
00:27:06,365 --> 00:27:08,925
Are you acting here?

418
00:27:08,925 --> 00:27:11,085
I've been grounded by my mom.

419
00:27:11,085 --> 00:27:12,665
I must go home on time after school

420
00:27:12,665 --> 00:27:14,565
for the next month.

421
00:27:14,565 --> 00:27:17,464
One yuan of my pocket money will be deducted for every minute late.

422
00:27:17,464 --> 00:27:19,615
I can't go anywhere else for the rest of the time.

423
00:27:19,615 --> 00:27:21,514
I can't even go to Zhang Qi's place.

424
00:27:21,515 --> 00:27:23,215
How about my place?

425
00:27:23,955 --> 00:27:27,505
She didn't mention it. But I guess I can't.

426
00:27:28,535 --> 00:27:31,275
It seems your mom is for real this time.

427
00:27:31,275 --> 00:27:34,055
If I knew it'd pay a high price to go out,

428
00:27:34,055 --> 00:27:36,795
I'd instead go to Xidan to have KFC.

429
00:27:37,515 --> 00:27:39,164
She'll cool down soon.

430
00:27:39,165 --> 00:27:40,575
It's hard this time.

431
00:27:40,575 --> 00:27:43,235
Take a look. My mom made

432
00:27:43,235 --> 00:27:45,465
this schedule the whole of last night.

433
00:27:45,465 --> 00:27:47,235
The time is tight and there are so many tasks.

434
00:27:47,235 --> 00:27:49,954
Obviously, it's to get rid of my freedom.

435
00:27:49,955 --> 00:27:52,665
I can't get a break until some days later.

436
00:27:52,665 --> 00:27:56,855
Then I'll plead for you.

437
00:27:57,715 --> 00:27:59,655
Forget it.

438
00:28:01,565 --> 00:28:02,965
Here you go.

439
00:28:06,575 --> 00:28:09,995
Did you buy it online for me?

440
00:28:09,995 --> 00:28:11,425
This is quite useful.

441
00:28:11,425 --> 00:28:13,955
You can record all the notes that you can't do in class.

442
00:28:13,955 --> 00:28:15,714
You can hear it anytime. It's very convenient.

443
00:28:15,715 --> 00:28:18,706
The point is to press the button next to it.

444
00:28:20,525 --> 00:28:25,070
<i>Sunian.</i>

445
00:28:29,335 --> 00:28:32,464
You used to say you'll get energetic when you hear my voice.

446
00:28:32,464 --> 00:28:34,776
That's why I recorded my voice.

447
00:28:34,776 --> 00:28:36,785
Do you feel energetic?

448
00:28:39,025 --> 00:28:41,085
I won't be tired after hearing it.

449
00:28:41,765 --> 00:28:43,185
Luckily I bought it early.

450
00:28:43,185 --> 00:28:46,935
Even the CPU has been confiscated.

451
00:28:46,935 --> 00:28:51,815
We said to leave some fond memories for our youth.

452
00:28:51,815 --> 00:28:55,135
Now there are only memories of me being grounded.

453
00:28:55,135 --> 00:28:56,924
You still have many years of youth.

454
00:28:56,925 --> 00:28:58,655
There are many chances.

455
00:28:58,655 --> 00:29:02,005
What if we go our separate ways in the future

456
00:29:02,005 --> 00:29:04,994
like what Zhang Qi said? What should we do?

457
00:29:06,125 --> 00:29:09,234
I finally understand why my mom

458
00:29:09,235 --> 00:29:11,565
doesn't want me to go abroad.

459
00:29:11,600 --> 00:29:18,600
I think if you go somewhere someday where I can't find you,

460
00:29:18,690 --> 00:29:21,315
I'll be very sad for sure.

461
00:29:21,315 --> 00:29:24,005
- I won't.
- Just in case.

462
00:29:24,005 --> 00:29:27,055
For me, it won't happen.

463
00:29:27,055 --> 00:29:31,155
I swear I'll always stay somewhere you can find.

464
00:29:44,985 --> 00:29:48,615
- Put it down gently.
- Okay.

465
00:29:52,925 --> 00:29:56,625
After work, ask Sunian to go to my place for dinner.

466
00:29:56,625 --> 00:29:57,855
Jin Ning isn't around, after all.

467
00:29:57,855 --> 00:29:59,034
We can have some drinks.

468
00:29:59,035 --> 00:30:00,035
Okay.

469
00:30:02,125 --> 00:30:04,125
When will Jin Ning come back?

470
00:30:04,125 --> 00:30:05,715
She went to her relative's house for several days.

471
00:30:05,715 --> 00:30:08,035
I think she'll be back soon.

472
00:30:08,035 --> 00:30:10,364
Why do I think it's not riveted?

473
00:30:10,365 --> 00:30:12,134
- Let's take a look.
- Take it slow.

474
00:30:12,134 --> 00:30:13,625
Here we go.

475
00:30:55,325 --> 00:30:57,215
You're back.

476
00:30:57,215 --> 00:31:00,675
Why didn't you tell me earlier? I could have picked you up.

477
00:31:00,675 --> 00:31:03,225
I didn't go to my relative's house.

478
00:31:03,885 --> 00:31:07,985
I just went to the hospital for an examination.

479
00:31:08,715 --> 00:31:11,585
- For...
- Zheng.

480
00:31:12,365 --> 00:31:14,605
I have cancer.

481
00:31:15,475 --> 00:31:17,315
It's terminal.

482
00:31:51,275 --> 00:31:53,225
<i>Zheng.</i>

483
00:32:38,475 --> 00:32:40,175
Is Mom asleep?

484
00:32:42,725 --> 00:32:46,855
Didn't I ask you to go home and rest?

485
00:32:50,135 --> 00:32:54,915
I feel uneasy at home alone.

486
00:33:06,245 --> 00:33:07,645
Dad.

487
00:33:09,665 --> 00:33:11,735
Mom will get well.

488
00:33:12,565 --> 00:33:14,165
Right?

489
00:33:46,175 --> 00:33:47,804
<i>It's almost spring.</i>

490
00:33:47,805 --> 00:33:51,754
<i>Everyone's heart has cooled down.</i>

491
00:33:52,655 --> 00:33:58,904
<i>Because the best Ms. Jin Ning in the world is ill.</i>

492
00:33:58,904 --> 00:34:01,654
<i>It seems that</i>

493
00:34:01,655 --> 00:34:04,934
<i>I haven't talked to Sunian for a long time.</i>

494
00:34:05,615 --> 00:34:07,945
<i>He has become more silent.</i>

495
00:34:07,945 --> 00:34:10,195
<i>So has Mr. Zheng.</i>

496
00:34:11,525 --> 00:34:14,105
<i>Just facing Ms. Jin Ning's illness</i>

497
00:34:14,105 --> 00:34:17,115
<i>has drained them too much.</i>

498
00:34:17,735 --> 00:34:21,055
<i>What makes me hate myself is</i>

499
00:34:21,055 --> 00:34:24,345
<i>that I find I'm afraid to see them</i>

500
00:34:24,345 --> 00:34:27,575
<i>and even more afraid to see Ms. Jin Ning.</i>

501
00:34:28,485 --> 00:34:32,385
<i>I'm afraid to see everything wonderful in the past</i>

502
00:34:32,385 --> 00:34:34,965
<i>suddenly collapse.</i>

503
00:34:50,775 --> 00:34:52,375
Xue.

504
00:34:56,165 --> 00:35:00,164
Didn't you go to join the Olympiad Mathematics training camp?

505
00:35:00,164 --> 00:35:01,564
Tomorrow will be a holiday.

506
00:35:01,565 --> 00:35:03,405
I'll go the day after tomorrow.

507
00:35:07,085 --> 00:35:09,675
Let's visit Ms. Jin Ning tomorrow.

508
00:35:12,695 --> 00:35:14,395
Okay.

509
00:35:18,895 --> 00:35:21,135
Haven't they come back yet?

510
00:35:23,855 --> 00:35:26,885
Since Ms. Jin Ning has been hospitalized,

511
00:35:26,885 --> 00:35:32,705
Mr. Zheng and Sunian seldom come home.

512
00:35:32,705 --> 00:35:34,605
They rented a bed at the hospital

513
00:35:34,605 --> 00:35:38,445
and take turns accompanying Ms. Jin Ning.

514
00:36:11,685 --> 00:36:14,025
Why do you get up so early?

515
00:36:24,255 --> 00:36:26,215
I'm making soup.

516
00:36:27,125 --> 00:36:30,025
I'm afraid it'll overflow. I have to watch over it.

517
00:36:37,735 --> 00:36:40,485
Do you think Jin Ning can drink it?

518
00:36:43,045 --> 00:36:45,775
Drink as much as she can.

519
00:36:46,685 --> 00:36:50,485
Zheng and Sunian need nutrition.

520
00:36:52,645 --> 00:36:56,265
Even they have no appetite.

521
00:36:56,265 --> 00:37:00,415
They only finished half of the meal you gave them.

522
00:37:01,295 --> 00:37:03,974
Why are you always being sarcastic here?

523
00:37:03,975 --> 00:37:06,644
If they don't eat, should I just let them be?

524
00:37:06,645 --> 00:37:10,584
If they don't eat something good, all of them will be sick.

525
00:37:24,775 --> 00:37:28,825
Why is God so unfair?

526
00:37:30,295 --> 00:37:32,565
Don't scold God.

527
00:37:32,565 --> 00:37:34,795
Beg him.

528
00:37:40,895 --> 00:37:44,505
